[{"Id": 1019075, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "In the same book it has been mentioned: If anybody is on deputation from the beginning of the journey and want to perform short Ziyarat then he should intend to perform Ziyarat from any of the particular Ziyarat on behalf of that person. Then offer 2 rakats namaz of Ziyarat and then recite this supplication…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Kitaab ‘Fee Ziyarat wa al-Adiyyah’ mein likkha huwa hai keh agar koi shakhs safar ki shuruwaat hi se kisi ki niyaabat mein ho aur woh makhsoos (khaas) ziyarat karna chahe to kisi bhi makhsoos ziyarat ko us shakhs ki niyaabat mein anjaam de. Phir 2 rakat namaz’e ziyarat padhe aur kahe…", "UrduDescription": "کتاب فی زیارت و الادیہ میں لکھا ہوا ہے کہ اگر کوئی شخص سفر کی شروعات ہی سے کسی کی نیابت میں ہو اور وہ مخصوص زیارت کرنا چاہے تو کسی بھی مخصوص زیارت کو اس شخص کی نیابت میں انجام دے، پھر ۲ رکعت نمازِ زیارت پڑھے اور کہے۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "Ar